# project overview

## introduction
this is a next.js-based frontend application for phono - an e-commerce platform. the project follows a modern react architecture using next.js app router and pages router (hybrid approach).

## main entry points
- the main app entry is [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx)
- the pages router entry is [src/pages/_app.tsx](mdc:src/pages/_app.tsx)

## key configuration files
- [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) - next.js configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - typescript configuration
- [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs) - postcss configuration

## primary folders
- `src/app` - contains app router components and layouts
- `src/pages` - contains pages router components
- `src/context` - contains react context providers
- `src/utils` - contains utility functions
- `src/api` - contains api related code and types
- `public` - contains static assets

refer to other rules for more detailed information about specific aspects of the project.
